room_title: Escape room "Fashion Week Nightmare" by Amaze: The Columbus Escape Experience in Columbus
review: The game masters were so fun and informative! you walk into a unique atmosphere that gets you even more elated for the room you are about to enter. I felt like I walked into a design studio when I walked into Fashion Week and easily entered the story. There were interesting puzzles in every corner of the room, I had a blast! I will definitely return to attempt another room, very worth the experience.
